{"tid":335062,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌撚曬你班覺得內向人係有問題嘅人","createTime":"2017-07-25T09:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T15:19:49.000Z","uid":130221,"like":92,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7689dada79d158f86364aa19a28253d4eddb478d","tid":335062,"uid":130221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"我屌你老味，我穿你老味個閪<br />\n知唔知呢個世界有外向人就有內向人<br />\n無可能個個都外向，人地天生係內向無可能逼人地改，特登要鳩人改搞撚到人地好似唔係做緊自己咁<br />\n利申：今日聽到有條友係背後話好靜，同人講我係個自閉仔，即刻忍唔撚到，一拳打撚到佢爆江，好撚爽"},{"pid":"15d68010ebe251c211ebffe8da18b42f478186cb","tid":335062,"uid":6294,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:45:13.000Z","msg":"無人在意你呀 醒下啦"},{"pid":"911de980b26d7544d1dcb3183ba3aff324093aae","tid":335062,"uid":130221,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人在意你呀 醒下啦</blockquote><br />\n係啊，無人在意，又會係人背後話鳩人"},{"pid":"f44cd81e6a3630da1d9469993aef586607fa8e05","tid":335062,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963f7510dabf42dc0fa0ca53a8ee8c6ba9f00773","tid":335062,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:12:23.000Z","msg":"你on9啫"},{"pid":"f1c52670227ed4f69fe716ff2d8019cad04e5849","tid":335062,"uid":7805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:14:03.000Z","msg":"做番自己最舒服<br />\n理撚得人點睇"},{"pid":"3ec1a7bed6b10007816380b04f6f27bf365f676b","tid":335062,"uid":130221,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你on9啫</blockquote><br />\n明明就係你on9，睇你個名就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e6620dc286b88d355a6eb9096461bb54c9c133","tid":335062,"uid":130221,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:24:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做番自己最舒服<br />\n理撚得人點睇</bl