?language=zh-tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ted.com%2Ftalks%2Fsusan_cain_the_power_of_introverts%2Fup-next%3Flanguage%3Dzh-tw&d=k6tLU5ag40v2dGNDhWlZkjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=81547824\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ted.com/talks/susan_cain_the_power_of_introverts/up-next?language=zh-tw</a>"},{"pid":"a0259ad9e905682bfe2df8b748b58dceccc9e883","tid":335062,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:22:16.000Z","msg":"打得好，打撚爆佢地個閪咀"},{"pid":"9e19f5f4f01c5f6af4d606f2c0179049105350a2","tid":335062,"uid":111860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:24:43.000Z","msg":"我最慘係屋企人成日話我內向唔出聲<br />\n但我真係同屋企人無乜話題，家姐都大過我好多<br />\n我同朋友都好多野講，但我都係覺得一個人先係最舒服<br />\n迫自己外向，多社交等於慢於自殺<br />\n無謂迫自己做啲自己唔想做既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ffa3df37486ff5fba5a7cadcb1de713d7740fe","tid":335062,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"好多矮仔唔憤氣衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd509a1cf526ec06accc0851b45ac4603896351","tid":335062,"uid":131220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你on9啫</blockquote><br />\n明明就係你on9，睇你個名就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6cc939ad9ff7d154cdb529156b8356537c176647","tid":335062,"uid":68589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"其實好多內向既人都有同人相處得好好<br />\n對人事有獨特既眼光 唔會招惹是非 都深得人欣賞<br />\n<br />\n其實你做好左自己 就唔需要太理會人地<br />\n如果人地真係對你有誤會 都總有一日時間會明白 適時既&quot;沉著&quot;會幫到你唔小<br />\n如果本身係人地質素低 就更加唔洗理"}]}